</taxonomicName>
Simon, 1893: 474. Type genus 
<taxonomicName id="974D2E71F6A576A26EC35C88CD76F9F9" class="Arachnida" family="Pholcidae" genus="Smeringopus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Smeringopus" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="61" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Smeringopus</taxonomicName>
